<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="bg-primary-500 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-primary-100">How we collect, use, and protect your information</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="card p-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 pb-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
      <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt mr-1"></i> Last updated: <%= helpers.formatDate(new Date()) %>
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, email address, and password when you register</li>
          <li><strong>Transaction Data:</strong> Purchase history, wallet transactions, and payment details</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, actions taken, browser type, and IP address</li>
          <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Support tickets and messages sent through our platform</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">Your information is used to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
          <li>Process transactions and deliver purchased accounts</li>
          <li>Send order confirmations and service updates</li>
          <li>Respond to support requests</li>
          <li>Detect and prevent fraud or abuse</li>
          <li>Improve our platform and user experience</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data.
          Account credentials are stored in encrypted form. Payment information is processed through secure third-party
          payment processors and is not stored on our servers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with trusted third-party services
          that help us operate our platform, such as payment processors. These partners are bound by
          confidentiality agreements and data processing standards.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We use session cookies to maintain your login state and provide essential platform functionality.
          These cookies are necessary for the platform to operate and cannot be disabled.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict the processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-3">
          To exercise these rights, please contact us through our <a href="/support" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 font-medium">support system</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes
          by posting the new policy on this page and updating the effective date.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
